ing: 1 (.7 ounce) package dry Italian-style salad dressing mix
des: "This is a tasty salad that is filling and goes great with just about any meal. It's perfect for summer barbecues."
ins:
In a large pot of salted boiling water, cook pasta until al dente, rinse under cold water and drain.
In a large bowl, combine the pasta, oil and salad dressing mix; toss together. Add vegetables and  cheese; mix well, cover and refrigerate over night.
